    $lang['about-head'] = 'ABOUT US';
    $lang['about-1'] = 'Vestamatic + CRE GmbH is a privately-owned company with its headquarters in Mönchengladbach, Germany. Vestamatic + CRE is a leading manufacturer of automation solutions to the shading market for over 40 years.';
    $lang['about-2'] = 'Vestamatic + CRE meets the needs of today’s buildings and future developments with in-house electronic design, manufacture and firmware development, scalable engineering solutions and expert support. With our focus on specification, commissioning and maintenance of contract and hospitality shading automation, we design, create and deliver one-stop-shop solutions with our partners. ';
    $lang['about-3'] = 'We run technology commonly used in buildings like KNX, BACNET, TCP/IP to connect and integrate shading into these. We run unique features in motors, wiring, automation, and service. Some of the biggest and most sophisticated buildings in the world are currently equipped with technology provided by Vestamatic + CRE.';
    $lang['about-4'] = 'Below you find technical product data for download and a request link for more information on these. Should you need a full scale project solution, please contact us. Please also visit our solution websites www.vestamaticcre.com and www.vcp-network.com.';
